data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! The epitome of country living yet still close to everything!!. As soon as you pull up to the property you'll immediately notice this peaceful and exquisite home and the large amount of space, Horses are allowed too!! Wrapped in hardy board and stone with touches of rough cut wood, tongue and groove porch ceilings.  As you enter the home into the large foyer with custom woodwork, The flooring throughout the home is a beautiful durable wood look tile. Continue through the house to the kitchen with High-end Cabinets, Rare custom Granite, and beautiful stainless appliances including gas cooktop!  A convenient full bathroom in the hallway for guests, cosy and comfortable living room. The spacious Master Suite features his & hers closets, Double custom vanity and HUGE custom walk in shower with multiple shower heads. This home also benefits from a multi functional room for additional living space, game room, office or craft room. It's a fabulous space!. The 2nd bedroom is complete with its own full bathroom and claw foot tub!.  This home has it all. Outside, the backyard is a dream with a premier 30 x 60 shop that will absolutely be the envy of all your friends. It comes complete with two 12ft W x 14ft H roll up doors, a separate side entry door and yet another 5ft x 8ft h roll up at the end of the shop for a mower & smaller toys, additionally it is fully spray foamed interior walls, custom L.E.D. motion lighting, and if that wasn't enough, there is well beside the shop and RV hook up. This property will not last call now for your private showing!
